    <summary>Terminal block explorer for Blocknet privacy blockchain</summary>
    <description>Terminal block explorer for Blocknet, a privacy-focused cryptocurrency. Built with ratatui. Connects to a running Blocknet daemon via its REST API.

Features:
- Dashboard with chain stats, wallet balance, mempool sparklines with history
- Mining controls with a plasma visualizer that reacts to hashrate
- 3D block grid view with spinning wireframe cubes
- Auto-detection of Blocknet data directory on all platforms
- Shockwave animation on block discovery

Requires a running Blocknet node with the API enabled.</description>
